SourceFileToReimport: The source file to import (path relative to the json script).
AssetTypeToReimport: The type of the asset to reimport. If only one such asset was imported, this is unambiguous.
AssetNameToReimport: If there were multiple assets of the above type imported, specify the concrete name here.
bSaveThenReloadImportedAssets: Determines whether imported assets should be saved and freshly reloaded after import.
